{"tid":2171789,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Die2nite: 40人殭屍團隊生存遊戲","createTime":"2020-08-24T07:51:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T11:23:20.000Z","uid":251366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c35b08f6d70d2fa2cb8d773de121cafa5578cabe","tid":2171789,"uid":251366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:51:06.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"maroon\"><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">DIE2NITE(40人殭屍團隊生存遊戲）</span></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9WqLmBX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9WqLmBX.jpg&h=15c43484&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家都知flash年尾就冇喇 呢隻game都好似唔會繼續做營運落去 所以想趁呢個機會玩返(雖然都有fans搞緊個非官方版 不過仲係test緊 玩住舊版先)<br />\n呢隻game其實已經出左好耐 但係一直仲有人玩緊 可能有人未玩過 抄返n年前高登個post介紹返先<br />\n<br />\n簡單介紹：<br />\n遊戲是由四十名玩家隨機進入城鎮，進行實時城鎮生存規劃拓荒，<br />\n每位玩家每日有限定的行動指數，但足夠你KEEP 住睇成日既，原因總會有勇者受困，有智者計錯數番唔到城<br />\n(依家最新仲要加埋玩家變屍鬼的內亂系統，同埋不怕死守門人系統)所以驚喜萬分，意外總是意料之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲主要語系係英文，但基本上都係D簡單字元，一查就有。<br />\n當你想知某一件物品有咩用既時候 亦有好齊既WIKI DATA BASE 俾你搵 <a href=\"http://d2nwiki.com/wiki/Main_Page\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd2nwiki.com%2Fwiki%2FMain_Page&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsmDcYOQIx6XO0JIcXsozN2c%3D&h=f5127a6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://d2nwiki.com/wiki/Main_Page</a><br />\n<br />\n試玩要點：<br />\n有點多，所以只能係度同各位簡單概括最最基本<br />\n如果你係新玩既/未接觸過既：<br />\n<br />\n1. 呢個遊戲新手的地圖係一個10X10 的地圖，如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HiTAJRp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHiTAJRp.png&h=82724de2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你一開始係位於主城位置，每日出去探下有無特殊地點同材料，<br />\n係彊屍大軍來之前(每晚固定一次)，搞好自己個城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每行新一格都可以搜索一次，原地唔郁則每兩小時一次(<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以做到早出晚歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n每日香港時間凌晨四五點個人唔係城入面，而你仲係出面探索緊既話就會自動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋每日都要開同關一次城門，大軍來到度門係開既，翌日將會全市死一半以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下呢張係城入面BANK有的物品圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uHAvxJ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuHAvxJ3.jpg&h=c4cd5072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 每日如果唔出去，城入面亦有更多可以做既野<br />\n包括： 去井口拎水每日一枝，去FORUM吹水要點玩，放行動點落建築，趁人出去偷人野，開門關門<br />\n記住一點就係，大家既目標先係個城可以生存幾耐，先到個人考慮，所以做自私精會被唾棄<br />\n同埋某D賤格行動係會紀錄係城入面，個個都見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 自行探索<br />\n唔係講笑，一隻遊戲要自己玩左先夠吸引，由我講晒咁你玩咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n通常一開始既城頂到五六日己經好勁，玩夠一定時間(100SOUL POINT)，<br />\n你既靈魂會變橙色就可以入老鬼城，同多D經驗豐富既人合作。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋遊戲有好多唔同既行動都會係滅城結算果下拎到獎章累積稱號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(包括：食人肉100次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />g ，被全市要求吊死N次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />g ，最後生還者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n有興趣玩既可以開返個tg gp一齊組隊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4959cf8cc5a481d9f5838ff343c8064c3bad17e8","tid":2171789,"uid":18444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:55:37.000Z","msg":"以前唔係叫last stand man 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 N年前玩過"},{"pid":"0ea4f49b1669dd129fa7eacf84d77a53f1850204","tid":2171789,"uid":251366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4959cf8cc5a481d9f5838ff343c8064c3bad17e8","tid":2171789,"uid":18444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:55:37.000Z","msg":"以前唔係叫last stand man 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 N年前玩過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T08:22:27.000Z","msg":"未聽過 可能我冇你咁早玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係知最後一個生存會有個distinction叫last man standing"},{"pid":"0fc91041a752afd842043e068f10c4e9842ec606","tid":2171789,"uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:45:33.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等我偷晒d野收埋自己屋企先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8254c0f213914059a03220a5719ee02a337b3b85","tid":2171789,"uid":125479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T18:38:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bf6e3caed08f9e83ce036e04ee08a157ed9fd00c","tid":2171789,"uid":251366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8254c0f213914059a03220a5719ee02a337b3b85","tid":2171789,"uid":125479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T18:38:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}